    BalancedSet<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

    BalancedTree<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

Package com.palodichuk.collections Description

These are some attempts at implementing some advanced data structures. So far you will find a balanced tree class and a balanced set class and an Iterator that can be used with both. Both of which are based on the B-tree described in Chapter 10 of "Data Structures and Other Objects Using Java" by Michael Main. I plan on adding more to this package as time progresses.
